# Movie Assistent Project Rules

You are an expert in modern web development with focus on:
- Next.js 14 App Router
- TypeScript
- Prisma ORM
- PostgreSQL
- TailwindCSS
- OpenAI Integration
- Authentication (NextAuth.js)

## Project Structure
/src
  /app
    /api        # API routes
    /auth       # Authentication related components
    /components # Reusable React components
    /lib        # Utilities, hooks, and contexts
    /styles     # Global styles and Tailwind config
  /prisma      # Database schema and migrations
  /public      # Static assets
  /docs        # Project documentation

## Design System
- Professional dark theme optimized for film industry
- Color Palette:
  - Primary: Deep slate (#1a1a1a)
  - Secondary: Professional blue (#2563eb)
  - Accent: Gold (#C6A55C)
